298
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:55,143
Yeah. We're done here.

299
00:14:57,929 --> 00:14:59,369
B-Barrett.

300
00:15:00,104 --> 00:15:02,683
You're the chief of surgery.
My rainmaker.

301
00:15:02,768 --> 00:15:06,113
I... Help me to save Chastain.

302
00:15:06,198 --> 00:15:07,910
Take the lowest-risk
elective surgeries

303
00:15:07,995 --> 00:15:09,862
and-and schedule them
as urgent.

304
00:15:11,026 --> 00:15:13,128
Okay, on one condition.

305
00:15:13,464 --> 00:15:16,613
Don't ever threaten my job again
or replace my face

306
