307
00:15:20,239 --> 00:15:21,620
Deal.

308
00:15:41,964 --> 00:15:43,346
Dr. Cain?

309
00:15:43,431 --> 00:15:45,168
<i>Is there something wrong?</i>

310
00:15:45,253 --> 00:15:46,468
I'm afraid so.

311
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:47,972
Listen, I know that I told you

